Instructions

(Each document has an id)

Create/Recreate the databade:

	psql -f documents.sql

Run the aplication:

	npm start

Get all documents:

	http://localhost:3000/api/documents

Get single document:

	http://localhost:3000/api/documents/id

Create a new document:

	$ curl --data "title=new_title&text=new_text" http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/documents

Update a document:

	$ curl -X PUT --data "title=updated_title&text=updated_text" http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/documents/id

Delete a document:

	$ curl -X DELETE http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/documents/id

